## Graveyard Sources
- §0.18 Sequential Testing Recipes (Anytime-Valid)
- §0.19 Evidence Ledger Schema (Machine-Readable)
- §12.1 Conformal Prediction [Tier A]
- §12.13 Online Change-Point Detection (ADWIN/CUSUM/Page-Hinkley) [Tier A]
